result.name: Ocean Super Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text: Great food,  very fresh prawns.  Noisy, though, like 98% of HK eateries.

Convenient location, spacious and comfortable, but not luxury, typical chinese restaurant. Serving time reasonable even in busy time! Look at the food, yummy and in big portions (this is big size). Highly recommended.

This is the second time we went to this restaurant, the food was quite big size and tastefully. We chose the hot pot dishes in the main menu. The manager recommended the seafood is very deliious and they were excellent with seafood cooking.  

We went there again on 21/3/2019, we ordered the 2 lobsters cooked with cheese source and e-fu noodles (  芝士焗龍虾，伊麵底、), Geoduck in whole boiled in with hotpot ( 白灼象拔蚌   ), they were expensive dishes, they Geoduck was not fresh and only half the size of the whole Geoduck. The lobsters were the same, half of the size and badly cooked. We were cheated by the restaurant. 

The overall cooking were awful in the seafood,  don't order seafood. Don't order seafood.
Reasonable price, decent food
fair seafood set menu. good quality and fair price... normally noise at most of the time.
